#define bn_set_high (  r,
a,
n    ) 
 

Value:

{ \
    if ((a)->top > (n)) \
        { \
        (r)->top=(a)->top-n; \
        (r)->d= &((a)->d[n]); \
        } \
    else \
        (r)->top=0; \
    (r)->neg=(a)->neg; \
    (r)->flags|=BN_FLG_STATIC_DATA; \
    bn_set_max(r); \
    }

#define mul (  r,
a,
bl,
bh,
c    ) 
 

Value:

{ \
    BN_ULONG l,h; \
 \
    h= (a); \
    l=LBITS(h); \
    h=HBITS(h); \
    mul64(l,h,(bl),(bh)); \
 \
      \
    l+=(c); if ((l&BN_MASK2) < (c)) h++; \
    (c)=h&BN_MASK2; \
    (r)=l&BN_MASK2; \
    }

#define mul64 (  l,
h,
bl,
bh    ) 
 

Value:

{ \
    BN_ULONG m,m1,lt,ht; \
 \
    lt=l; \
    ht=h; \
    m =(bh)*(lt); \
    lt=(bl)*(lt); \
    m1=(bl)*(ht); \
    ht =(bh)*(ht); \
    m=(m+m1)&BN_MASK2; if (m < m1) ht+=L2HBITS((BN_ULONG)1); \
    ht+=HBITS(m); \
    m1=L2HBITS(m); \
    lt=(lt+m1)&BN_MASK2; if (lt < m1) ht++; \
    (l)=lt; \
    (h)=ht; \
    }

#define mul_add (  r,
a,
bl,
bh,
c    ) 
 

Value:

{ \
    BN_ULONG l,h; \
 \
    h= (a); \
    l=LBITS(h); \
    h=HBITS(h); \
    mul64(l,h,(bl),(bh)); \
 \
      \
    l=(l+(c))&BN_MASK2; if (l < (c)) h++; \
    (c)=(r); \
    l=(l+(c))&BN_MASK2; if (l < (c)) h++; \
    (c)=h&BN_MASK2; \
    (r)=l; \
    }

#define sqr64 (  lo,
ho,
in    ) 
 

Value:

{ \
    BN_ULONG l,h,m; \
 \
    h=(in); \
    l=LBITS(h); \
    h=HBITS(h); \
    m =(l)*(h); \
    l*=l; \
    h*=h; \
    h+=(m&BN_MASK2h1)>>(BN_BITS4-1); \
    m =(m&BN_MASK2l)<<(BN_BITS4+1); \
    l=(l+m)&BN_MASK2; if (l < m) h++; \
    (lo)=l; \
    (ho)=h; \
    }
